g and when I asked him what it was =E2=80=93 he said =E2=80=98oh its from S=
quid Games=E2=80=99 I was initially surprised as aware of
 the graphic nature of the Netflix show and explained to him, he shouldn=E2=
=80=99t be watching these shows as they are not designed for children. I di=
dn=E2=80=99t want to make a big thing of it or cause him upset or embarrass=
ment but mentioned I would speak with you both in
 regard to it. <u></u><u></u></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u></u>=C2=A0<u></u></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I am not sure whether you are aware that he has acce=
ss to material such as this or whether you have a Netflix account or he has=
 just stumbled across it on YouTube. Perhaps you may want to check your par=
ental settings to further prevent
 access to such material, obviously the nature of this will then set algori=
thms to bring up similar materials. Could you also check with him what he h=
as accessed and ensure he is not scared or disturbed by this and know it is=
 not appropriate to discuss in class.
 Tereza our school councellor is also on hand to discuss this further with =
him if need be and has experience of handling such matters<u></u><u></u></p=
